    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Let's say you set the default value of a `RefinementList` on the `\"animals\"` facet to `[\"cats\"]`. When you first load the page, this default value won't be shown in the URL. The only way to deselect the `\"cats\"` value in this case is to explicitly set the `\"animals\"` facet value to an empty array. Just removing the entire facet value won't do, because then the default value will be selected again.\n",
    "created_at": "2016-10-20T12:17:57Z",
    "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/1286#issuecomment-255089649",
    "id": 255089649,
