    "body": "> The only way to deselect the \"cats\" value in this case is to explicitly set the \"animals\" facet value to an empty array\n\n@mthuret In any way, we just need to keep this behavior, since it's feasible for people to do so, it's a feature (not just a weird edge case)\n",
